gobblin.source.extractor.extract.kafka

Class KafkaPartition

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.source.extractor.extract.kafka.KafkaPartition

  • public final class KafkaPartition
extends java.lang.Object
    A kafka topic partition. Two partitions are considered equivalent if they have the same topic name and partition id. They may have different leaders.
